backend.grid.BoundsHandler.name: Infinite Bounds
backend.grid.BoundsHandler.description: Allows grid to expand to accommodate out of bounds coordinates.

backend.grid.BoundsHandler.name: Toroidal Bounds

backend.grid.BoundsHandler.name: Finite Bounds

backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.name: Blind
backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.description: The attacker gives any neighboring unit the Blinded modifier

range.name: Square Adjacent
range.description: This pattern of square coordinates is composed of all square coordinates adjacent to the origin.

backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.name: Silence
backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.description: Removes all temporary abilities from any neighboring unit

backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.name: Consume
backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.description: The attacker deals damage to the defender. If the defender dies, the user heals for the amount of damage dealt, and the user takes the defender's place. (Does not count as movement)

backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.name: Suicide Squad, Attack!
backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.description: The attacker sacrifices itself to deal massive damage to all neighboring enemy units.

backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.name: Sword
backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.description: The attacker hits 3 times for 5 damage on any neighboring unit

backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.name: Full Heal
backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.description: The attacker fully heals any neighboring unit

backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.name: Bow
backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.description: The attacker hits 2 times for 7 dmage on any unit in a straight line away from the attacker

range.name: Square Rays
range.description: This pattern of square coordinates is composed of all square coordinates on 4 rays centered at the origin

backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.name: Set Fire to Cell
backend.unit.properties.ActiveAbility.description: The attacker sets fire to the cell they are occupying.

range.name: Square Single Cell
